{"tid":667182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咬腳皮魚全部死亡 揭男顧客全身浸魚池偷偷小便","createTime":"2018-05-16T13:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T11:23:05.000Z","uid":177556,"like":829,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"60f9484f9c6e0274c46790b924dd5267610b990e","tid":667182,"uid":177556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:40:59.000Z","msg":"星島日報報道】內地網傳廣東一間魚療館過千條小魚突然離奇死亡，店主翻查閉路電視後發現，竟是一名男顧客做魚療時小便所致。該男子拒絕賠償，辯稱「我怎麼知道這小魚這麼脆弱，我只是尿失禁而已！」<br />\n<br />\n　　涉事男顧客近日與朋友到魚療館做溫水魚療，讓魚咬走腳部死皮。豈料他浸了幾分鐘後，竟整個人浸在魚池里。小魚向他游過去，5分鐘後，魚群忽然全部反肚，男子察覺有異與朋友離開。<br />\n<br />\n魚療館老闆發現魚群死亡，遂翻看閉路電視片段，相信男子在魚池內小便所致。老闆向對方要求賠償3萬元人民幣，但男子反駁：「我怎麼知道這小魚這麼脆弱，我只是尿失禁而已，你這魚我老家到處都是，還要這麼貴，你以為有錢就了不起呀」，並反指老闆敲詐。老闆最終報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/214052_0635e3c36049d86348bc356c0055da2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F214052_0635e3c36049d86348bc356c0055da2c.png&h=85ab7a80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6eea8e300989bf667d19fab8d296a18a331f4c48","tid":667182,"uid":77461,"like":650,"dislike":4,"score":646,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"死毒撚"},{"pid":"f1ed7fa2ecdbbec5c19866b86d5abac0f8ab71a1","tid":667182,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56745ab351e965762dc4dc3278ca9713856e220a","tid":667182,"uid":82382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e90bc8f666a9db